WEBVTT
X-TIMESTAMP-MAP=MPEGTS:900000,LOCAL:00:00:00.000

00:00:19.769 --> 00:00:21.938 position:50% align:center
[INFERNAL snarls]

00:00:22.022 --> 00:00:23.273 position:50% align:center
[FIREFIGHTER A]
There's a fire in the Arakawa

00:00:23.356 --> 00:00:24.482 position:50% align:center
Shopping District.

00:00:24.566 --> 00:00:26.693 position:50% align:center
Seems it was caused
by a single infernal.

00:00:26.776 --> 00:00:28.445 position:50% align:center
Unfortunately,
there's been a casualty.

00:00:28.528 --> 00:00:30.030 position:50% align:center
An employee of the fruit stand.

00:00:30.113 --> 00:00:32.198 position:50% align:center
Understood.

00:00:32.282 --> 00:00:34.409 position:50% align:center
One casualty already?

00:00:34.492 --> 00:00:37.787 position:50% align:center
Make sure that you're
prepared, Sister.

00:00:37.871 --> 00:00:39.539 position:50% align:center
Sir.

00:00:39.622 --> 00:00:42.584 position:50% align:center
Spider Net, engage!

00:00:42.667 --> 00:00:44.586 position:50% align:center
The road's closed off now.

00:00:44.669 --> 00:00:45.503 position:50% align:center
We're good here!

00:00:45.587 --> 00:00:47.339 position:50% align:center
--[explosion]
--[BOTH gasp]

00:00:51.259 --> 00:00:53.178 position:50% align:center
Now!

00:00:53.261 --> 00:00:56.973 position:50% align:center
[snarls]

00:00:57.057 --> 00:00:59.809 position:50% align:center
[IRIS]
The flame is the soul's breath.

00:00:59.893 --> 00:01:02.771 position:50% align:center
The black smoke is
the soul's release.

00:01:02.854 --> 00:01:04.773 position:50% align:center
Ashes thou wert and art.

00:01:04.856 --> 00:01:09.652 position:50% align:center
May thy soul return...
to the great flame of fire.

00:01:09.736 --> 00:01:12.405 position:50% align:center
Launching Special
Extinguishing Grenade!

00:01:17.911 --> 00:01:19.579 position:50% align:center
[OBI]
<i>L치tom</i> !

00:01:24.167 --> 00:01:26.127 position:50% align:center
The Infernal has now
been put to rest.

00:01:26.211 --> 00:01:27.337 position:50% align:center
[MAN A]
Sister!

00:01:27.420 --> 00:01:29.756 position:50% align:center
Is the Infernal...?
My wife, she...

00:01:29.839 --> 00:01:32.342 position:50% align:center
[IRIS]
Oh, the next of kin.

00:01:32.425 --> 00:01:36.221 position:50% align:center
My wife, she's
received salvation?

00:01:36.304 --> 00:01:39.057 position:50% align:center
She's been granted the divine
mercy of Sol, hasn't she?

00:01:39.140 --> 00:01:40.600 position:50% align:center
[IRIS gasps]

00:01:42.811 --> 00:01:44.479 position:50% align:center
Yes.

00:01:44.562 --> 00:01:46.147 position:50% align:center
Your wife has passed
on peacefully

00:01:46.231 --> 00:01:48.858 position:50% align:center
into the embrace of the Lord.

00:01:54.614 --> 00:01:56.366 position:50% align:center
[SHINRA]
Either I'm misreading something,

00:01:56.449 --> 00:01:59.202 position:50% align:center
or the scriptures are incorrect
on several major points.

00:01:59.285 --> 00:02:01.746 position:50% align:center
The Holy Sol Temple might have
some secret connection

00:02:01.830 --> 00:02:03.790 position:50% align:center
to the Evangelist.

00:02:07.043 --> 00:02:09.754 position:50% align:center
I can't dwell on
worldly matters.

00:03:47.102 --> 00:03:48.520 position:50% align:center
[OBI]
Okay.

00:03:48.603 --> 00:03:50.480 position:50% align:center
Those flechettes, as well?

00:03:50.563 --> 00:03:53.108 position:50% align:center
Correct, sir.
And that's all of it.

00:03:53.191 --> 00:03:55.694 position:50% align:center
I guess we've had a lot
of callouts lately,

00:03:55.777 --> 00:03:59.072 position:50% align:center
which means we're behind
on baptizing the gear.

00:03:59.155 --> 00:04:01.991 position:50% align:center
But the Sister can't carry
all of this by herself.

00:04:02.075 --> 00:04:03.326 position:50% align:center
Huh?

00:04:03.410 --> 00:04:04.869 position:50% align:center
You want me to go with her
to the Central Church

00:04:04.953 --> 00:04:06.413 position:50% align:center
to baptize our equipment?

00:04:06.496 --> 00:04:09.541 position:50% align:center
[OBI] Yeah. It's also called
the Baptism Church.

00:04:09.624 --> 00:04:11.793 position:50% align:center
You've never been there
before, have you?

00:04:11.876 --> 00:04:13.128 position:50% align:center
[SHINRA]
No, sir.

00:04:13.211 --> 00:04:15.547 position:50% align:center
[OBI] All the gear we need
baptized is in there.

00:04:15.630 --> 00:04:17.090 position:50% align:center
[SHINRA]
Got it, sir.

00:04:17.173 --> 00:04:19.676 position:50% align:center
[IRIS] Excuse me.
I'm ready to go when you are.

00:04:19.759 --> 00:04:20.927 position:50% align:center
[SHINRA]
Looking forward to it!

00:04:21.011 --> 00:04:24.806 position:50% align:center
Yeah! Let's go
rock n' roll! Yay!

00:04:24.889 --> 00:04:27.934 position:50% align:center
Too freakin' cute!

00:04:28.018 --> 00:04:29.936 position:50% align:center
[SHINRA]
I'm going on a date.

00:04:30.020 --> 00:04:32.272 position:50% align:center
A church date with Sister Iris.

00:04:32.355 --> 00:04:33.898 position:50% align:center
[IRIS] That stuff isn't
too heavy, is it?

00:04:33.982 --> 00:04:35.984 position:50% align:center
Nope, not for me!

00:04:36.067 --> 00:04:38.278 position:50% align:center
Must be tough doing
this alone, huh?

00:04:38.361 --> 00:04:41.156 position:50% align:center
[IRIS] There usually isn't
this much to carry.

00:04:44.367 --> 00:04:45.744 position:50% align:center
I need to start hitting the gym

00:04:45.827 --> 00:04:47.537 position:50% align:center
so the rest of you
don't show me up.

00:04:47.620 --> 00:04:51.124 position:50% align:center
[SHINRA] Her skin is like
cream and so supple.

00:04:51.207 --> 00:04:55.128 position:50% align:center
No! This is wrong.
I can't look at her like this!

00:04:55.211 --> 00:04:59.299 position:50% align:center
It's not just off limits,
that Power Cobra is forbidden!

00:05:02.969 --> 00:05:05.930 position:50% align:center
[SHINRA] So this is the
Baptism Church, huh?

00:05:08.266 --> 00:05:12.395 position:50% align:center
Oh, wow. Is all this
water used for baptisms?

00:05:12.479 --> 00:05:14.731 position:50% align:center
It'll take a little time
for me to finish,

00:05:14.814 --> 00:05:17.233 position:50% align:center
so feel free to have a
look around the church.

00:05:17.317 --> 00:05:19.903 position:50% align:center
[SHINRA]
Okay. I'll see you in a bit.

00:05:22.947 --> 00:05:24.699 position:50% align:center
[SHINRA sighs]

00:05:24.783 --> 00:05:26.743 position:50% align:center
I guess there's not gonna
be any time for a stroll

00:05:26.826 --> 00:05:28.328 position:50% align:center
with the Sister.

00:05:28.411 --> 00:05:31.581 position:50% align:center
What did I expect? This is work.

00:05:33.958 --> 00:05:35.960 position:50% align:center
This place is really beautiful.

00:05:36.044 --> 00:05:39.881 position:50% align:center
But it still has the stain
of the Evangelist on it.

00:05:39.964 --> 00:05:43.259 position:50% align:center
Sister Iris is acting
as cheerful as usual,

00:05:43.343 --> 00:05:47.806 position:50% align:center
but there's a sadness
inside her smile.

00:05:47.889 --> 00:05:49.307 position:50% align:center
If something's bothering her,

00:05:49.391 --> 00:05:52.852 position:50% align:center
I'd be happy to help her
out in any way I can.

00:05:52.936 --> 00:05:54.521 position:50% align:center
O merciful and hallowed Lord

00:05:54.604 --> 00:05:56.648 position:50% align:center
who shineth brightly
in the heavens,

00:05:56.731 --> 00:06:00.235 position:50% align:center
may those that reach thy
presence receive thy blessing...

00:06:00.318 --> 00:06:02.779 position:50% align:center
[IRIS] If the Holy Sol Temple
was originally founded

00:06:02.862 --> 00:06:07.492 position:50% align:center
by the Evangelist, then who
exactly am I praying to?

00:06:07.575 --> 00:06:11.079 position:50% align:center
Sister Iris.
Something's distracting you.

00:06:11.162 --> 00:06:12.706 position:50% align:center
[IRIS]
Oh, I'm sorry.

00:06:12.789 --> 00:06:15.000 position:50% align:center
Please grant the blessing
of thy baptism to all--

00:06:15.083 --> 00:06:17.085 position:50% align:center
These grounds are
really something else.

00:06:17.168 --> 00:06:19.754 position:50% align:center
[LI] Well, if it isn't
Kusakabe from the 8th.

00:06:19.838 --> 00:06:22.424 position:50% align:center
Hello, Lieutenant!
It's good to see you!

00:06:22.507 --> 00:06:24.134 position:50% align:center
I didn't expect to
run into you here.

00:06:24.217 --> 00:06:25.510 position:50% align:center
Uh.

00:06:26.970 --> 00:06:30.098 position:50% align:center
I'm just helping get some
of our equipment baptized.

00:06:30.181 --> 00:06:31.182 position:50% align:center
[LI]
I'm glad to hear the 8th

00:06:31.266 --> 00:06:33.143 position:50% align:center
is still committed
to such practices.

00:06:33.226 --> 00:06:34.853 position:50% align:center
What do you mean by that?

00:06:34.936 --> 00:06:37.022 position:50% align:center
Surely you've heard
the rumors by now.

00:06:37.105 --> 00:06:39.649 position:50% align:center
About the Temple
and the Evangelist.

00:06:39.733 --> 00:06:41.067 position:50% align:center
Well, unfortunately,

00:06:41.151 --> 00:06:43.820 position:50% align:center
it's led to some units
neglecting their sacred rites.

00:06:43.903 --> 00:06:44.779 position:50% align:center
[gasps]

00:06:44.863 --> 00:06:46.573 position:50% align:center
Karim, for example.

00:06:46.656 --> 00:06:50.827 position:50% align:center
It's not hard to tell, his faith
is definitely being tested.

00:06:50.910 --> 00:06:53.621 position:50% align:center
[SHINRA] Is that what's
bothering the Sister?

00:06:53.705 --> 00:06:55.498 position:50% align:center
I'd like to know your
thoughts, Lieutenant.

00:06:55.582 --> 00:06:56.750 position:50% align:center
[gasps]

00:06:59.836 --> 00:07:01.963 position:50% align:center
[LI] I'll admit, when I heard
the Holy Sol Temple

00:07:02.047 --> 00:07:05.884 position:50% align:center
may have been founded by the
Evangelist, I was shocked.

00:07:05.967 --> 00:07:09.763 position:50% align:center
However, the Temple exalts the
glory of the Sun and its fire,

00:07:09.846 --> 00:07:11.264 position:50% align:center
not the Evangelist.

00:07:11.348 --> 00:07:12.891 position:50% align:center
I've worshipped
the Sun all my life,

00:07:12.974 --> 00:07:16.519 position:50% align:center
and as long as it remains,
so will my faith.

00:07:16.603 --> 00:07:19.773 position:50% align:center
On the other hand, I've had
a startling revelation.

00:07:19.856 --> 00:07:21.900 position:50% align:center
If the Evangelist
was simply a fraud,

00:07:21.983 --> 00:07:24.319 position:50% align:center
she'd be enriching herself
and setting herself up

00:07:24.402 --> 00:07:26.529 position:50% align:center
to be worshipped by the masses.

00:07:26.613 --> 00:07:27.906 position:50% align:center
[gasps]

00:07:27.989 --> 00:07:29.741 position:50% align:center
That's true.

00:07:29.824 --> 00:07:31.159 position:50% align:center
[LI]
But the reality is,

00:07:31.242 --> 00:07:34.996 position:50% align:center
the Evangelist lurks in
the shadows, out of sight.

00:07:35.080 --> 00:07:37.874 position:50% align:center
So that gives some
credence to what's said

00:07:37.957 --> 00:07:40.919 position:50% align:center
to be her ultimate goal:
The end of the world.

00:07:41.002 --> 00:07:43.880 position:50% align:center
You're saying our
faith's dangerous?

00:07:48.343 --> 00:07:51.680 position:50% align:center
[LI]
Faith is crucial.

00:07:51.763 --> 00:07:54.432 position:50% align:center
People need to believe
in something.

00:07:57.143 --> 00:07:58.561 position:50% align:center
[SHINRA]
Tell me, Lieutenant.

00:07:58.645 --> 00:08:00.021 position:50% align:center
Was it your faith
that spurred you

00:08:00.105 --> 00:08:03.274 position:50% align:center
to protect Lieutenant Karim
without a second thought?

00:08:06.277 --> 00:08:07.904 position:50% align:center
[LI]
I suppose it was.

00:08:07.987 --> 00:08:10.532 position:50% align:center
I strongly believe in
the Holy Sol Temple,

00:08:10.615 --> 00:08:13.368 position:50% align:center
as well as in Lieutenant Karim.

00:08:13.451 --> 00:08:19.082 position:50% align:center
Losing something or someone
so dear is devastating.

00:08:19.165 --> 00:08:21.209 position:50% align:center
If you have the
power to believe,

00:08:21.292 --> 00:08:23.294 position:50% align:center
you can save your friends.

00:08:23.378 --> 00:08:26.715 position:50% align:center
Having the power to believe.

00:08:26.798 --> 00:08:28.550 position:50% align:center
That'll be your duty now...

00:08:28.633 --> 00:08:30.719 position:50% align:center
Remember, no matter
what goes down here,

00:08:30.802 --> 00:08:32.012 position:50% align:center
Asakusa is your town.

00:08:32.095 --> 00:08:34.723 position:50% align:center
The people aren't waiting
for me. It's Beni...

00:08:34.806 --> 00:08:36.766 position:50% align:center
As Soldiers, you
should understand.

00:08:36.850 --> 00:08:38.685 position:50% align:center
This life of mine
isn't worth much,

00:08:38.768 --> 00:08:41.980 position:50% align:center
so if I can help Waka,
I'll put it on the line.

00:08:42.063 --> 00:08:44.024 position:50% align:center
[SHINRA]
The 7th has that power

00:08:44.107 --> 00:08:47.277 position:50% align:center
because their strength
comes from their hearts.

00:08:47.360 --> 00:08:51.281 position:50% align:center
But if you lose the
things you believe in...

00:08:51.364 --> 00:08:53.658 position:50% align:center
Apologies for making you wait.

00:08:53.742 --> 00:08:57.037 position:50% align:center
I was a little distracted
and Sister scolded me for it.

00:08:57.120 --> 00:09:00.582 position:50% align:center
[SHINRA] Oh, it's okay.
Happens to everyone.

00:09:00.665 --> 00:09:04.002 position:50% align:center
[SHINRA] So even she's
shaken up by all this.

00:09:04.085 --> 00:09:05.211 position:50% align:center
[SHINRA]
Well, wanna head back?

00:09:05.295 --> 00:09:07.047 position:50% align:center
Oh, I, uh--

00:09:08.173 --> 00:09:11.968 position:50% align:center
I have a quick little stop that
I'd like to make on the way.

00:09:13.762 --> 00:09:14.846 position:50% align:center
[SHINRA]
This place.

00:09:14.929 --> 00:09:16.973 position:50% align:center
[IRIS] Yes, the National
Holy Sol Cemetery

00:09:17.057 --> 00:09:18.767 position:50% align:center
is where the clergy get buried.

00:09:18.850 --> 00:09:20.352 position:50% align:center
Whoa.

00:09:20.435 --> 00:09:24.606 position:50% align:center
I always stop by here after
I'm done with the baptisms.

00:09:24.689 --> 00:09:27.859 position:50% align:center
It's mainly to visit the shrine
of the Sisters from the convent

00:09:27.942 --> 00:09:30.195 position:50% align:center
where I grew up.

00:09:30.278 --> 00:09:33.365 position:50% align:center
[SHINRA]
Wow! Look at all the sunflowers!

00:09:33.448 --> 00:09:36.951 position:50% align:center
[IRIS] Aren't they wonderful?
They bloom facing the sun.

00:09:37.035 --> 00:09:37.786 position:50% align:center
You see?

00:09:37.869 --> 00:09:39.079 position:50% align:center
They're planted near shrines

00:09:39.162 --> 00:09:40.955 position:50% align:center
so the dead can find
the way to the Sun.

00:09:41.039 --> 00:09:43.208 position:50% align:center
To guide their spirits.

00:09:45.251 --> 00:09:48.254 position:50% align:center
[IRIS] Here, do you mind
praying with me?

00:09:48.338 --> 00:09:50.298 position:50% align:center
[SHINRA]
Not at all!

00:09:52.133 --> 00:09:53.468 position:50% align:center
[IRIS grunts]

00:09:56.137 --> 00:09:58.056 position:50% align:center
Well, that's a pretty
flashy shrine.

00:09:58.139 --> 00:10:01.059 position:50% align:center
I'm afraid that would
be Hibana's doing.

00:10:01.142 --> 00:10:03.019 position:50% align:center
How can the dead
rest with all this?

00:10:03.103 --> 00:10:05.188 position:50% align:center
I wouldn't have expected her.

00:10:05.271 --> 00:10:07.023 position:50% align:center
These flowers are still fresh.

00:10:07.107 --> 00:10:09.150 position:50% align:center
Looks like she just
came by recently.

00:10:09.234 --> 00:10:10.735 position:50% align:center
Surprising as it may seem,

00:10:10.819 --> 00:10:14.030 position:50% align:center
she truly did love everyone
from the convent.

00:10:14.114 --> 00:10:16.908 position:50% align:center
She comes here to
visit quite frequently.

00:10:16.991 --> 00:10:19.744 position:50% align:center
But subtlety is not her forte.

00:10:21.705 --> 00:10:23.540 position:50% align:center
[IRIS]
I hope you're all doing well.

00:10:23.623 --> 00:10:27.627 position:50% align:center
Sister Clematis, please
remember to not overindulge.

00:10:27.711 --> 00:10:31.464 position:50% align:center
And Sister Sakura,
try not to stay up too late.

00:10:31.548 --> 00:10:32.632 position:50% align:center
Next time I'll come see you

00:10:32.716 --> 00:10:35.802 position:50% align:center
before Hibana does
her razzle-dazzle.

00:10:37.387 --> 00:10:38.805 position:50% align:center
[SHINRA]
Sister Iris?

00:10:38.888 --> 00:10:40.557 position:50% align:center
[IRIS]
Uh. Yes?

00:10:40.640 --> 00:10:43.351 position:50% align:center
[SHINRA] I hope I'm
not outta line here...

00:10:44.686 --> 00:10:46.438 position:50% align:center
But if there's
anything troubling you,

00:10:46.521 --> 00:10:49.274 position:50% align:center
I'd be more than happy to help.

00:10:49.357 --> 00:10:51.776 position:50% align:center
I mean, it's the
Evangelist, right?

00:10:51.860 --> 00:10:54.195 position:50% align:center
My goodness, is it
really that obvious?

00:10:54.279 --> 00:10:56.573 position:50% align:center
I guess hiding things
isn't my forte.

00:10:56.656 --> 00:10:59.200 position:50% align:center
You're good at always
pushing Vulcan's buttons.

00:10:59.284 --> 00:11:01.369 position:50% align:center
Cutting to the chase
on what you want.

00:11:01.453 --> 00:11:04.622 position:50% align:center
I'd never accuse you
of being hard to read.

00:11:04.706 --> 00:11:07.792 position:50% align:center
Uh, but hear me out! I'm not
saying that's a bad thing!

00:11:07.876 --> 00:11:12.088 position:50% align:center
You're honest and sincere.
People love that about you!

00:11:13.548 --> 00:11:18.511 position:50% align:center
[IRIS] Shinra, what do you think
about the Holy Sol Temple?

00:11:18.595 --> 00:11:21.056 position:50% align:center
And those of us who
strongly believe in it?

00:11:21.139 --> 00:11:22.182 position:50% align:center
The people like me?

00:11:22.265 --> 00:11:23.475 position:50% align:center
[gasps]

00:11:23.558 --> 00:11:24.184 position:50% align:center
What do I--?

00:11:24.267 --> 00:11:25.727 position:50% align:center
[SISTER B screams]

00:11:25.810 --> 00:11:27.979 position:50% align:center
[SHINRA]
What's that?

00:11:28.063 --> 00:11:30.482 position:50% align:center
Father, no.

00:11:30.565 --> 00:11:31.983 position:50% align:center
[IRIS]
What happened?

00:11:32.067 --> 00:11:35.111 position:50% align:center
[SISTER B]
Father. All of a sudden, he--

00:11:35.195 --> 00:11:37.447 position:50% align:center
[SHINRA]
An Infernal.

00:11:37.530 --> 00:11:38.823 position:50% align:center
But how?

00:11:38.907 --> 00:11:41.951 position:50% align:center
He's so steadfast in his faith.
He's always in prayer.

00:11:42.035 --> 00:11:46.081 position:50% align:center
[SHINRA] I'll take care of him.
Please, keep back!

00:11:49.209 --> 00:11:52.253 position:50% align:center
[roars]

00:11:53.338 --> 00:11:55.006 position:50% align:center
[SHINRA]
Sister! The prayer!

00:11:55.090 --> 00:11:56.383 position:50% align:center
[IRIS]
Right, of course!

00:11:56.466 --> 00:11:59.552 position:50% align:center
Um. The flame is
the soul's breath.

00:11:59.636 --> 00:12:02.639 position:50% align:center
The black smoke is
the soul's release.

00:12:02.722 --> 00:12:06.351 position:50% align:center
Ashes thou wert and art.
May thy soul return...

